"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-simone-biless-funny-way-of-dealing-with-injury-paris-games-loved-fans\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The GOAT, Simone Biles, was back in action at the Olympics on Sunday as she kicked off her Paris Games in style by lookinglike her dominant selfin Sunday's qualifying session.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wassome concern about Biles's health, however, as she was seen limping a bit after warming up for the floor routine.\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles's coach, Cecile Landi, later said the gymnast was dealing with a calf injury that she suffered a few weeks ago.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles did not let that slow her down at all, however.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only did she push through the pain, she seemed to have fun with it as she was seen smiling while crawling on the mat so she did not have to put any pressure on her calf.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles will always be famous.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dealing with an injury at the Olympics and having fun & finding joy while pushing through it.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What an icon \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0091pic.twitter.com/eBz9er8Zta  Fans loved that:  SHES SO SILLY \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00ad\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00ad\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00adhttps://t.co/K4bNK3MBVa  This moment is yet another reason why I absolute LOVE & ADORE Simone Biles.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a badass & what leadership!https://t.co/mmTCOs0hG9  The fact that I too have crawled instead of walking bc of ankle pain but I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m just a regular schmegular person \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082 thanks for the representation, Simone!!!!\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LOLhttps://t.co/QAvvCIwOn3  \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0082https://t.co/EpcMETlYiL  The grit.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The passion.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fight.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopping around on one leg and crawling back to the VT line for warm-ups.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vermont\", \"score\": 0.9934479040381086, \"rank\": 0.006542827352162065, \"text\": \"VT\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vermont\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vermont\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The woman you are!!!\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She did it for herself, and I am so honored to be able to watch!#ArtisticGymnastics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00af\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00af\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00af#PARIS2024https://t.co/8RpxzJb1kP  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Andy Nesbitt is the assistant managing editor of audience engagement at Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.1199106346117153e